                            p.text-muted Powered by OpenSensorHub
                            p.text-muted A public OpenSensorHub instance exposing live sensors, datastreams, and observations through the CSAPI Part 1 and Part 2 endpoints, including SensorML system descriptions and SWE Common observation payloads.
                            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='https://129-80-248-53.sslip.io/sensorhub/api' title='Landing page' target='_blank')
