                            p.text-muted A public CSAPI demonstrator from 52°North built on pygeoapi. Hosts curated example collections, systems, and observations and is a useful target for testing pygeoapi-based clients and tooling.
                            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='https://csa.demo.52north.org/' title='Landing page' target='_blank')
                                i.fa.fa-link
